<i>noun</i>: 침통 [침통], 비참 [비ː참], 도탄 [도탄], 곤궁 [곤ː궁] <i>verb</i>: 괴롭히다 [괴로피다/궤로피다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>침통 [침통]</dt><br>
<dd>distress; sadness; mournfulness</dd><br>
<dd>슬픔이나 걱정 등으로 마음이 몹시 괴롭거나 슬픔.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of feeling deep agony or sadness from sorrow, worry, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>비참 [비ː참]</dt><br>
<dd>misery; wretchedness; distress</dd><br>
<dd>견딜 수 없을 정도로 슬프고 끔찍함.</dd><br>
<dd>An unbearably sad and dreadful feeling.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>도탄 [도탄]</dt><br>
<dd>distress</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 어렵고 고통스러운 상황이나 생활.</dd><br>
<dd>A situation of or living in extreme suffering and pain.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곤궁 [곤ː궁]</dt><br>
<dd>1. poverty; destitution</dd><br>
<dd>가난하여 궁핍함.</dd><br>
<dd>Being poor and destitute.</dd><br>
<dd>2. distress; hardship; difficulty</dd><br>
<dd>곤란하고 딱한 처지.</dd><br>
<dd>Being in a dangerous or pathetic situation.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>괴롭히다 [괴로피다/궤로피다]</dt><br>
<dd>torment; harass; distress</dd><br>
<dd>몸이나 마음이 편하지 않고 아프게 하거나 고통스럽게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make someone feel uncomfortable, painful, or agonized physically or mentally.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>